<!--
Explaining the properties used for theme-ing

- background: main background.
- foreground: the content area on top of the background.
- text: regular text views and text in input fields.
- text_hint: the hint color in input fields.
- text_solid: text that is displayed on top of any "solid" areas.
- solid: the main theme color, usually a strong color.
- active: the color of active input components.
- toolbar: usually matches the solid color.
- accent: used for interactive text-links.
-->

